\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces VSR pipeline: a non-differentiable verifier produces structured feedback (per-macro severity scalar, pairwise overlap graph, boundary vector); a selector turns it into a soft mask; a 100-step force integrator (post-mode) or structured RePaint (intra-mode) updates only offending macros. No backbone retraining; no differentiable surrogate.}}{2}{figure.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
